  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406600/extras/e4c5608b46af202ab34de4dacad9a408.avif?t=1737059515\" width=600 height=100 /></span>   </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a snow-covered world filled with dangerous monsters, take command of a unique team of magical ducks in an epic battle! Combine powers, plan your strategy, and build the ultimate flock as you face unpredictable challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406600/extras/1eb79c4d94d9550f4e8215749b789326.webp?t=1737059515\" width=600 height=50 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406600/extras/36b914845c4a7381220f4aea073fd029.webp?t=1737059515\" width=600 height=50 /></span>Control up to 6 ducks in your flock, each with unique abilities to customize your strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406600/extras/f2100f816c8dddee9a4e363219dc419c.webp?t=1737059515\" width=600 height=50 /></span>Cast dazzling spells and battle hordes of enemies while dodging their attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406600/extras/b864ffaeea05e3218230da6ae02d05b5.poster.avif?t=1737059515\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406600/extras/b864ffaeea05e3218230da6ae02d05b5.webm?t=1737059515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406600/extras/b864ffaeea05e3218230da6ae02d05b5.mp4?t=1737059515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406600/extras/a9369cb9b75a36a479efe64b69b1bcac.webp?t=1737059515\" width=600 height=50 /></span>Buy new ducks and swap them at the end of each level to tailor your team for upcoming challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406600/extras/36ce206b3ea0c404d6ca1a241c83c61d.poster.avif?t=1737059515\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406600/extras/36ce206b3ea0c404d6ca1a241c83c61d.webm?t=1737059515\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3406600/extras/36ce206b3ea0c404d6ca1a241c83c61d.mp4?t=1737059515\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the perfect mix of strategy and magical chaos in this unique and captivating game. Can you lead your ducks to victory?</p>",
